[src:custom-elements/api-window] Decodes a string of data which has been encoded using base-64 encoding.
[src:custom-elements/api-window] Creates a base-64 encoded ASCII string from a string of binary data.
[src:custom-elements/api-window] Enables you to cancel a callback previously scheduled with `Window.requestAnimationFrame`.
[src:custom-elements/api-window] Enables you to cancel a callback previously scheduled with `Window.requestIdleCallback`.
